0.1.name: wordpress/rank-checker-by-surfing-panda
0.1.description: This plugin provides data on the various keywords that bring visitors to your Wordpress site. Each time you receive a visit from Google, this plugin will record the keyword they searched for. It will also record your website's ranking for that keyword. This data will be displayed on the Wordpress Administration pages.
